AUTHORS
=======

hostnamed - org.freedesktop.hostname1 over plain D-Bus, no systemd
required. Maintained for Slackware and other non-systemd Linux
systems.

Maintainer
----------
Nathaniel Russell <naterussell83@gmail.com>
    Project creator and maintainer. Initial implementation of the
    daemon, D-Bus interface, PolKit policy, meson build, and
    SlackBuild packaging. GitHub: @nater1983

Contributors
------------
Anagnostakis Ioannis <elahistos@yahoo.gr>
    PR #1 (rizitis/main): fixed a PolKit authorization bypass and a
    JSON-escaping bug in the D-Bus interface; converted PolKit
    authorization to an asynchronous flow; added dedicated PolKit
    actions for GetProductUUID/GetHardwareSerial; added
    defence-in-depth validation in the machine-info writer.

----

If you've contributed to hostnamed and don't see your name here,
please open a pull request adding yourself, or file an issue at
https://github.com/nater1983/hostnamed/issues so this file can be
corrected.
